Hey!

123
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:07,640
Khem!

124
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,320
Let go of me! What are you trying to do?

125
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:14,120
I'd like to hug my own wife.

126
