My dear wife,

127
00:09:19,375 --> 00:09:21,415
tonight is the nuptial night.

128
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:26,440
How about we do things
like married couples do?

129
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:29,960
Hold on.

130
00:09:30,936 --> 00:09:32,256
In the evening,

131
